3 likes, 0 comments - hemang_kapadia on November 13, 2023: "Happy Birthday Olga Kostyantynivna -  My Filmy Duniya
Olga Kostyantynivna Kurylenko is a Ukrainian and French actress and former model. Born and raised in Berdyansk, Kurylenko moved to Paris at the age of 16 to pursue a modelling career. After starting her acting career in 2004, she had her breakthrough film role in the action-thriller Hitman. 
Born: 14 November 1979 (age 43 years), Berdyans'k, Ukraine
Spouse: Damian Gabrielle (m. 2006–2007), Cedric Van Mol (m. 2000–2004)
Height: 1.75 m
Parents: Marina Alyabusheva, Konstantin Kurylenko
Children: 1
